# Planner UI Lock

Do **not** change layout, colors, spacing, typography, or visual styling unless the user explicitly asks for a UI/visual change.

## Canonical reference

- **Design spec**: `src/components/RecipeCard.reference.tsx`
- **Style tokens**: `src/lib/plannerUiStyles.ts`
- **Live planner**: `src/components/PlannerView.tsx` (behavior/data only — keep visual parity with the reference)
- **Shell & nav**: `src/components/AppShell.tsx`, `src/components/BottomNav.tsx`
- **Theme colors**: `src/app/globals.css` (`emerald`, `cyan`, `violet`, `coral`)

## Allowed without UI approval

- Wiring real data, state, and business logic
- Bug fixes that preserve the existing look
- Adding features **below** the v0 bento cards without altering cards above

## Forbidden without explicit user approval

- Changing Tailwind classes on planner components
- Moving, resizing, or reordering UI sections
- New color accents outside the established palette rules
- Replacing bento cards, day selector, profile toggles, or ingredient checklist styling

## Color rules (must preserve)

- **Macro numbers only**: emerald / cyan / violet / coral with glow (`macroColorClasses`)
- **Ingredient weights**: zinc-100 / zinc-400 — never cyan or macro colors
- **Profile toggles**: emerald and violet active backgrounds only
- **Day selector active pill**: emerald on zinc-900 track
- **Checkboxes**: emerald fill with zinc-950 check icon
- **Bottom nav active tab**: emerald with drop-shadow glow
